n’s goals this quarter? This year? How are you</span></div><div class="t m0 x19 h8 y846 ff6 fs3 fc2 sc0 ls0 wsd0a">merging product goals (if any) with the technical goals? Does your organi-</div><div class="t m0 x19 h8 y847 ff6 fs3 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">zation have a mandate that is well understood by the teams?</div><div class="t m0 x8e h12 ya4 ff9 fsd fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">MANA<span class="_ _b"></span>GING MANA<span class="_ _b"></span>GERS <span class="_ _12"> </span>| <span class="_ _c"> </span>157</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[2.314815,0.000000,0.000000,2.314815,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
